":"2013-04-17T13:41:43.897-0500","updated":"2013-04-17T13:41:43.897-0500"},{"self":"http://jira.codehaus.org/rest/api/2/issue/145578/comment/323855","id":"323855","author":{"self":"http://jira.codehaus.org/rest/api/2/user?username=krosenvold","name":"krosenvold","emailAddress":"krosenvold@apache.org","avatarUrls":{"16x16":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&ownerId=krosenvold&avatarId=11127","24x24":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?size=small&ownerId=krosenvold&avatarId=11127","32x32":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?size=medium&ownerId=krosenvold&avatarId=11127","48x48":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?ownerId=krosenvold&avatarId=11127"},"displayName":"Kristian Rosenvold","active":true},"body":"Unfortunately the patch breaks file mode for directories on unix and mac os:\r\n\r\norg.codehaus.plexus.archiver.zip.ZipArchiverTest#testCreateArchive and especially line 265 seems to not work any more. If I unzip the created zip file with os-level unzip (preserving as much attributes as possible), I get the following result:\r\n\r\ntarget/output/archive1.zip with plexus-io 2.0.6:\r\nd---rwx---  4 kristian  staff  136 Apr 17 18:27 groupwritable\r\ndr-x------  4 kristian  staff  136 Apr 17 18:27 main\r\n-rw-r-----  1 kristian  staff   23 Apr 17 18:27 one.txt\r\ndr-x------  3 kristian  staff  102 Apr 17 18:47 site\r\ndr-x------  6 kristian  staff  204 Apr 17 18:27 test\r\n-rw-rw-r--  1 kristian  staff   59 Apr 17 18:27 two.txt\r\ndrwxrwxrwx  3 kristian  staff  102 Apr 17 18:27 worldwritable\r\n\r\ntarget/output/archive1.zip with your plexus-io patch:\r\ntotal 16\r\ndr--------  4 kristian  staff  136 Apr 17 18:27 groupwritable\r\ndr--------  4 kristian  staff  136 Apr 17 18:27 main\r\n-rw-r-----  1 kristian  staff   23 Apr 17 18:27 one.txt\r\ndr--------  3 kristian  staff  102 Apr 17 18:47 site\r\ndr--------  6 kristian  staff  204 Apr 17 18:27 test\r\n-rw-rw-r--  1 kristian  staff   59 Apr 17 18:27 two.txt\r\ndr--------  3 kristian  staff  102 Apr 17 18:27 worldwritable\r\n\r\n\r\nAs you can see the \"groupwriteable\" directory has incorrect permissions.\r\n\r\nI will revert these fixes on master and move them to a branch PLXCOMP220; please submit further pull requests to this branch(es)","updateAuthor":{"self":"http://jira.codehaus.org/rest/api/2/user?username=krosenvold","name":"krosenvold","emailAddress":"krosenvold@apache.org","avatarUrls":{"16x16":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&ownerId=krosenvold&avatarId=11127","24x24":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?size=small&ownerId=krosenvold&avatarId=11127","32x32":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?size=medium&ownerId=krosenvold&avatarId=11127","48x48":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?ownerId=krosenvold&avatarId=11127"},"displayName":"Kristian Rosenvold","active":true},"created":"2013-04-17T14:29:41.236-0500","updated":"2013-04-17T14:29:41.236-0500"},{"self":"http://jira.codehaus.org/rest/api/2/issue/145578/comment/323859","id":"323859","author":{"self":"http://jira.codehaus.org/rest/api/2/user?username=sergei_ivanov","name":"sergei_ivanov","emailAddress":"sergei_ivanov@mail.ru","avatarUrls":{"16x16":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&ownerId=sergei_ivanov&avatarId=11312","24x24":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?size=small&ownerId=sergei_ivanov&avatarId=11312","32x32":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?size=medium&ownerId=sergei_ivanov&avatarId=11312","48x48":"http://jira.codehaus.org/secure/useravatar?ownerId=sergei_ivanov&avatarId=11312"},"displayName":"Sergei Ivanov","active":true},"body":"I do apologise for that. It looks like my attempt to deduplicate attribute merging backfired. I have been looking at the changes for the last 15 minutes, and I think I know where it went wrong. I shall try to sort it out on the branch, with more unit tests is needed.","updateAuthor":{"self":"http://jira.codehaus.org/rest/api/2/user?username=sergei_ivanov",